gospel-grinder
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:A derog. term popular in the early 20C. for a street-preacher, evangelist, esp. a member of the Salvation Army. (Perhaps mainly used  by Truth, in its fondness for alliterative epithets and dislike of Salvationists.  Cf gospel-thumper.
